wikipedia_page.main: Oliver Taylor  (1869 – 1945) was a Welsh international footballer. He was part of the Wales national football team between 1893 and 1894, playing 4 matches. He played his first match on 18 March 1893 against Scotland and his last match on 24 March 1894 against Scotland .
